---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Submit Module">
  <section class="markdown-panel markdown-body">
    <h1>Submit Module</h1>
    <p>Submit modules by creating or transferring a public repository under the Xposed-Modules-Repo organization.</p>
    <p>The repository should include a valid Android APK release whose tag starts with the version code, for example <code>123-1.2.3</code>.</p>
    <p>Use the following optional files to improve the listing:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>README.md</code> for the module page.</li>
      <li><code>SUMMARY</code> for the module card summary.</li>
      <li><code>SOURCE_URL</code> for source links.</li>
      <li><code>ADDITIONAL_AUTHORS</code> for extra author metadata.</li>
      <li><code>HIDE</code> to hide the module from listing pages.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
